  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5446569">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5446569/" class="title-link">我读的是电子版</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5446569"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ireno/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1060899-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ireno/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Reno</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-05-29"
      class="main-meta">2012-05-29 19:19:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5446569_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读中国哲学家的思考，比N个世纪前德译英、英再译汉的体系哲学要舒服得多，特别是身处作者同样的历史背景之中，对于作者所发出的感叹总是有心领神会的感觉。  系统的哲学是作者多年来学术思考的结晶，也是与其作品读者的对话。  挖个坑，一定填上。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5446569/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 3没用</span>
